# Development Workflow

## Available Scripts
- `npm run dev` - Start development server with Turbopack
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run start` - Start production server
- `npm run lint` - Run ESLint

## Development Server
- Uses Next.js 15 with Turbopack for faster development
- Hot reloading enabled
- TypeScript compilation with strict mode
- Tailwind CSS compilation

## Code Quality
- ESLint configuration follows Next.js recommendations
- TypeScript strict mode enforced
- Consistent code formatting expected
- Component testing recommended

## File Naming Conventions
- Use kebab-case for file names
- Use PascalCase for component names
- Use camelCase for functions and variables
- Use UPPER_SNAKE_CASE for constants

## Git Workflow
- Feature branches for new development
- Descriptive commit messages
- Pull request reviews for main branch
- Keep commits atomic and focused

## Dependencies
- All UI components from Radix UI ecosystem
- Form handling with React Hook Form + Zod
- Styling with Tailwind CSS v4
- Error tracking with StackFrame
- Database integration with Neon (serverless)
